description:
This is a 21 minute workout called 'Guided Daily Breathwork Routine To Help Smile And Feel Joy I 3 Rounds' from the channel Breathe With Sandy.
The workout falls under Rest/Breathing exercises and Rest/Meditation.
It's suitable for Beginner fitness levels.
The workout has a The Zen Flow and The Deep Recharge vibe.
The technique difficulty is Beginner.
The effort required is Light.
